scene.message:
Yukino: Not that it matters,{nl}
but the chests in this tower{nl}
sure have an odd shape.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Somehow Ayase's gotten{nl}
hungry. Aren't there any{nl}
chests with food in them?{waitkey}

Nanjo: Medicines and items{nl}
only have meaning when used.{nl}
We mustn't let them go to{waitkey}waste.

Brown: No matter how much{nl}
time we've got, it's never{nl}
enough, really.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even as we stand here, that{nl}
"Eternal Night" or whatever{nl}
might
